{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need to fix Weld CDI injection issues in a Jakarta EE application. The problem is that Lombok's `@AllArgsConstructor` generates constructors without `@Inject`, but Weld requires `@Inject` on constructors for CDI injection.\n\nThe fix: For every file that is a CDI-managed bean (has `@ApplicationScoped`, `@RequestScoped`, `@Dependent`, or `@Singleton` annotation, OR is a JAX-RS `@Path` resource) AND also has `@AllArgsConstructor`, I need to:\n\n1. Change `@AllArgsConstructor` to `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)` \n2. Add `import jakarta.inject.Inject;` if not already present\n\nThe base directory is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java\n\nHere are the files that need fixing (they are both CDI beans AND have @AllArgsConstructor):\n\nCDI beans with @AllArgsConstructor:\n- org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/entity/EntityUtils.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/provider/SlugifySlugProvider.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/validator/ModelValidator.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/user/UserModelBuilder.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/tag/TagBuilder.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/comment/CommentBuilder.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/article/ArticleModelBuilder.java\n\nJAX-RS resources with @AllArgsConstructor:\n- org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/TagsResource.java\n\nDomain feature implementations with @AllArgsConstructor (these are also CDI beans):\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/UpdateUserImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/UpdateArticleBySlugImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/UnfollowUserByUsernameImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/UnfavoriteArticleImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/LoginUserImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/IsFollowingUserImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/IsArticleFavoritedImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FollowUserByUsernameImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindUserByUsernameImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindUserByIdImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindTagsImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindTagsByNameCreateIfNotExistsImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindMostRecentArticlesByFilterImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindCommentsByArticleSlugImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindCommentByIdAndAuthorImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindArticlesByFilterImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindArticleTagsImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindArticleBySlugImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindArticleByIdImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FindArticleByAuthorAndSlugImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/FavoriteArticleImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/DeleteCommentImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/DeleteArticleBySlugImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/CreateUserImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/CreateTagImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/CreateSlugByTitleImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/CreateCommentImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/CreateArticleImpl.java\n- org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/ArticleFavoritesCountImpl.java\n\nFor each file:\n1. Read the file\n2. Check if it has `@AllArgsConstructor` AND is a CDI bean (has @ApplicationScoped, @RequestScoped, @Dependent, @Singleton, or @Path annotation)\n3. If so:\n   a. Replace `@AllArgsConstructor` with `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)`\n   b. Add `import jakarta.inject.Inject;` if not already present (add it near other jakarta imports or near other import statements)\n4. Do NOT modify files that are pure data classes (no CDI scope annotation and no @Path) - these just use @AllArgsConstructor for convenience and don't need @Inject\n\nIMPORTANT: Also check the domain/feature/impl files - they likely have @ApplicationScoped. Fix them too.\n\nAlso IMPORTANT: Some files might not have @AllArgsConstructor but still need CDI fixes. The repository classes (ArticleRepositoryPanache, etc.) already use field injection with @Inject, so they should be fine. Focus only on classes that use @AllArgsConstructor for constructor injection.\n\nPlease read each file first before editing it. Process ALL the files listed above. Report back which files you modified and which you skipped (and why)."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014TjWyNSwtQyHDxeJKs7YUX","session_id":"4d21e41c-7b8c-412a-ac18-df8336bdf9ca","uuid":"193e5c06-9910-4939-b992-43cdca7aa6b7"}
