{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_013YNiymSTA2QresjPvBV7Gd","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! The changes have been applied correctly. Now let me create a summary of all the changes made.\n\n## Summary of Changes\n\nI have successfully fixed the Weld CDI proxy issues in your Jakarta EE application by adding `@NoArgsConstructor` annotations to all classes that use `@AllArgsConstructor` with constructor injection. This allows Weld to create proxies for normal-scoped beans and JAX-RS resources.\n\n### Files Modified (8 total):\n\n#### ApplicationScoped CDI Beans (3 files):\n1. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/entity/EntityUtils.java**\n   - Added `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;`\n   - Added `@NoArgsConstructor` before `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)`\n\n2. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/provider/SlugifySlugProvider.java**\n   - Added `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;`\n   - Added `@NoArgsConstructor` before `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)`\n\n3. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java**\n   - Added `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;`\n   - Added `@NoArgsConstructor` before `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)`\n\n#### JAX-RS Resource Classes (5 files):\n4. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java**\n   - Added `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;`\n   - Added `@NoArgsConstructor` before `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)`\n\n5. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java**\n   - Added `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;`\n   - Added `@NoArgsConstructor` before `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)`\n\n6. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java**\n   - Added `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;`\n   - Added `@NoArgsConstructor` before `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)`\n\n7. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java**\n   - Added `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;`\n   - Added `@NoArgsConstructor` before `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)`\n\n8. **/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/TagsResource.java**\n   - Added `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;`\n   - Added `@NoArgsConstructor` before `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)`\n\n### Files Analyzed but Not Modified:\n- **JwtTokenProvider.java** - Already uses field injection only (no @AllArgsConstructor)\n- **BCryptHashProvider.java** - No constructor or injection annotations needed\n- **All Repository classes** (ArticleRepositoryPanache, UserRepositoryPanache, CommentRepositoryPanache, TagRepositoryPanache, FollowRelationshipRepositoryPanache, FavoriteRelationshipRepositoryPanache, TagRelationshipRepositoryPanache) - All use field injection only\n- **AbstractPanacheRepository.java** - Uses field injection only\n\n### What This Fixes:\nThe `@NoArgsConstructor` annotation allows Weld to create client proxies for:\n- `@ApplicationScoped` beans (normal-scoped) which require proxies for lazy instantiation and contextual behavior\n- JAX-RS `@Path` resources that are CDI-managed and need to support dependency injection\n\nWithout the no-arg constructor, Weld cannot create proxies and will throw errors at runtime when trying to instantiate these beans."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4d21e41c-7b8c-412a-ac18-df8336bdf9ca","uuid":"9e964fa6-6b03-4216-a1d5-99cb6f71e0c7"}
