{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_0165dyxpMqGdFzapdLjCmoqU","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_015LVkMAFTDHgz1mz9pszJUp","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Fix @NoArgsConstructor force=true","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"I need to change `@NoArgsConstructor` to `@NoArgsConstructor(force = true)` on specific CDI bean files that have `final` fields. The `force = true` option tells Lombok to initialize final fields with default values (null for objects, 0 for primitives, etc.).\n\nThe base directory is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java\n\nOnly modify these 8 files (they have both @NoArgsConstructor and @AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject) with final fields):\n\n1. org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/entity/EntityUtils.java\n2. org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/provider/SlugifySlugProvider.java\n3. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java\n4. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java\n5. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java\n6. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java\n7. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java\n8. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/TagsResource.java\n\nFor each file:\n1. Read the file\n2. Replace `@NoArgsConstructor` with `@NoArgsConstructor(force = true)` \n3. IMPORTANT: Do NOT modify any other files (like entity files, response files etc which also have @NoArgsConstructor but don't have the issue)\n\nReport back which files were modified."}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":870,"cache_read_input_tokens":95522,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":870,"ephemer