{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01UeArWwQQb6WxcnhUxSDxYj","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! The modifications are complete. Now let me create a summary report of all the changes made.\n\n## Summary Report\n\nI have successfully added CDI scope annotations to all 5 JAX-RS resource classes for RESTEasy-CDI discovery. Here's what was done:\n\n### Modified Files (All 5 Resource Classes):\n\n1. **ArticlesResource.java** \n   - Path: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java`\n   - Added: `import jakarta.enterprise.context.RequestScoped;`\n   - Added: `@RequestScoped` annotation before class declaration\n   - Annotation order: `@RequestScoped` → `@NoArgsConstructor` → `@AllArgsConstructor` → `@Path(\"/articles\")`\n\n2. **UsersResource.java**\n   - Path: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java`\n   - Added: `import jakarta.enterprise.context.RequestScoped;`\n   - Added: `@RequestScoped` annotation before class declaration\n   - Annotation order: `@RequestScoped` → `@NoArgsConstructor` → `@AllArgsConstructor` → `@Path(\"/users\")`\n\n3. **UserResource.java**\n   - Path: `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java`\n   - Added: `import jakarta.enterprise.context.RequestScoped;`\n   - Added: `@RequestScoped` annotation before class declaration\n   - Annotation order: `@RequestScoped` → `@NoArgsConstructor` → `@AllArgsConstructor` → `@Path(\"/user\")`\n\n4. **ProfilesResource.java**\n   - Path: