{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01WLdFZH9acdWTJDePyy4uJ6","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01WpA5rct3PmoAakFYjyGxkK","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Convert CDI beans to field injection","subagent_type":"general-purpose","prompt":"I need to convert 8 CDI-managed classes from Lombok constructor injection to plain CDI field injection. The problem is that Weld CDI doesn't work well with `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)` combined with `@NoArgsConstructor(force = true)` on `final` fields - it throws \"WELD-000810: Cannot place qualifiers on final fields\".\n\nThe fix: For each of these 8 files, I need to:\n1. Remove `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)` annotation\n2. Remove `@NoArgsConstructor(force = true)` annotation  \n3. Remove `import lombok.AllArgsConstructor;` and `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;` if no longer used\n4. Change all `private final SomeType fieldName;` to `@Inject private SomeType fieldName;` (remove `final`, add `@Inject`)\n5. Add `import jakarta.inject.Inject;` if not already present\n6. For fields with CDI qualifiers (like `@NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper`), keep the qualifier and add `@Inject`\n\nThe base directory is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java\n\nFiles to modify:\n\n1. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java\n2. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java\n3. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java\n4. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java\n5. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/TagsResource.java\n6. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java\n7. org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/entity/EntityUtils.java\n8. org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/provider/SlugifySlugProvider.java\n\nExample transformation for a resource:\n\nBEFORE:\n```java\nimport lombok.AllArgsConstructor;\nimport lombok.NoArgsConstructor;\n...\n\n@RequestScoped\n@NoArgsConstructor(force = true)\n@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)\n@Path(\"/users\")\npublic class UsersResource {\n  private final CreateUser createUser;\n  private final LoginUser loginUser;\n  private final TokenProvider tokenProvider;\n```\n\nAFTER:\n```java\nimport jakarta.inject.Inject;\n...\n\n@RequestScoped\n@Path(\"/users\")\npublic class UsersResource {\n  @Inject private CreateUser createUser;\n  @Inject private LoginUser loginUser;\n  @Inject private TokenProvider tokenProvider;\n```\n\nFor ArticlesResource.java specifically, there's a field with a CDI qualifier:\n```java\n@NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n```\nThis should become:\n```java\n@Inject @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper private ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n```\n\nIMPORTANT: Read each file before editing. Make sure to handle all fields correctly. Report all changes made."}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":821,"cache_read_input_tokens":146442,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":821,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":894},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4d21e41c-7b8c-412a-ac18-df8336bdf9ca","uuid":"934ab2eb-775b-4351-acc3-a595717df709"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"I need to convert 8 CDI-managed classes from Lombok constructor injection to plain CDI field injection. The problem is that Weld CDI doesn't work well with `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)` combined with `@NoArgsConstructor(force = true)` on `final` fields - it throws \"WELD-000810: Cannot place qualifiers on final fields\".\n\nThe fix: For each of these 8 files, I need to:\n1. Remove `@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)` annotation\n2. Remove `@NoArgsConstructor(force = true)` annotation  \n3. Remove `import lombok.AllArgsConstructor;` and `import lombok.NoArgsConstructor;` if no longer used\n4. Change all `private final SomeType fieldName;` to `@Inject private SomeType fieldName;` (remove `final`, add `@Inject`)\n5. Add `import jakarta.inject.Inject;` if not already present\n6. For fields with CDI qualifiers (like `@NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper`), keep the qualifier and add `@Inject`\n\nThe base directory is: /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src/main/java\n\nFiles to modify:\n\n1. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ArticlesResource.java\n2. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UsersResource.java\n3. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/UserResource.java\n4. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/ProfilesResource.java\n5. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/TagsResource.java\n6. org/example/realworldapi/application/web/resource/utils/ResourceUtils.java\n7. org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/hibernate/entity/EntityUtils.java\n8. org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/provider/SlugifySlugProvider.java\n\nExample transformation for a resource:\n\nBEFORE:\n```java\nimport lombok.AllArgsConstructor;\nimport lombok.NoArgsConstructor;\n...\n\n@RequestScoped\n@NoArgsConstructor(force = true)\n@AllArgsConstructor(onConstructor_ = @Inject)\n@Path(\"/users\")\npublic class UsersResource {\n  private final CreateUser createUser;\n  private final LoginUser loginUser;\n  private final TokenProvider tokenProvider;\n```\n\nAFTER:\n```java\nimport jakarta.inject.Inject;\n...\n\n@RequestScoped\n@Path(\"/users\")\npublic class UsersResource {\n  @Inject private CreateUser createUser;\n  @Inject private LoginUser loginUser;\n  @Inject private TokenProvider tokenProvider;\n```\n\nFor ArticlesResource.java specifically, there's a field with a CDI qualifier:\n```java\n@NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n```\nThis should become:\n```java\n@Inject @NoWrapRootValueObjectMapper private ObjectMapper objectMapper;\n```\n\nIMPORTANT: Read each file before editing. Make sure to handle all fields correctly. Report all changes made."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01WpA5rct3PmoAakFYjyGxkK","session_id":"4d21e41c-7b8c-412a-ac18-df8336bdf9ca","uuid":"fbd90266-795f-4dcd-a0cf-a1541b020535"}
