{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01DQf84iEkQzb1ADHKFJA1QJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01CoasTLqMjoZUamJHataGM4","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Investigate login and article errors","prompt":"In the codebase at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__quarkus__jakarta/run_1/output/src, I need to debug two issues:\n\n1. **Login always returns 401 Unauthorized** - even with correct credentials after successful registration\n2. **Create Article returns 500** \n\nFor the login issue, find and read these files in order to understand the login flow:\n- LoginRequest.java (the DTO)\n- UsersResource.java (the login method)\n- LoginUser.java (the domain feature interface)\n- The LoginUser implementation class\n- The UserRepository implementation (look for how `findByEmail` or similar is implemented)\n- BCryptHashProvider or whatever password hashing service is used\n\nFor the article issue, find and read:\n- ArticlesResource.java (the create method)\n- The CreateArticle implementation class\n- The ArticleRepository implementation\n\nReturn the COMPLETE contents of each file you find. Pay special attention to:\n- Whether EntityManager transactions are being managed properly (begin/commit/rollback)\n- Whether password verification is working correctly\n- Whether there are any issues with the user lookup query","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":689,"cache_read_input_tokens":94698,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":689,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":436},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4d21e41c-7b8c-412a-ac18-df8336bdf9ca","uuid":"1f0363b8-d688-44a0-9af2-1c066cf9c666"}
