{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01FXzLs6UJeyPzpenWu4oztg","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete: Quarkus to Standalone Jakarta EE\n\n**Result: 67/67 smoke tests passing**\n\nThe RealWorld (Conduit) API has been successfully migrated from Quarkus to a standalone Jakarta EE stack:\n\n- **RESTEasy 6.2.12** for JAX-RS\n- **Weld SE 5.1.3** for CDI\n- **Hibernate ORM 6.6.4** for JPA\n- **Undertow 2.3.18** as the embedded HTTP server\n\n### Key challenges resolved during migration:\n\n1. **CDI injection** - Converted from Lombok constructor injection to CDI field injection for Weld proxy compatibility\n2. **Request scope** - Changed from `@RequestScoped` to `@Dependent` since Weld SE doesn't have servlet request context\n3. **EntityManager sharing** - Implemented `ThreadLocal<EntityManager>` pattern so all repositories within the same request share one EM instance\n4. **Transaction management** - Created `TransactionalInterceptor` with resource-local transactions, added `@Transactional` to all endpoints\n5. **Resource discovery** - Explicitly registered resources/providers via `setScannedResourceClasses`/`setScannedProviderClasses`\n6. **Jackson configuration** - Created `ObjectMapperContextResolver` for `WRAP_ROOT_VALUE`/`UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE`\n7. **Security** - Created `SecurityFilter` + `RolesAllowedFilter` for JWT auth and `@RolesAllowed` processing\n8. **Jandex conflict** - Excluded jandex 2.x from Weld, used smallrye jandex 3.2.0 for Hibernate 6.x compatibility"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":782,"cache_read_input_tokens":138713,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":782,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":430},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4d21e41c-7b8c-412a-ac18-df8336bdf9ca","uuid":"0d17e22e-7697-4203-be40-e75668cc966d"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":6732881,"duration_api_ms":4541112,"num_turns":357,"result":"All tasks are complete. Here's a summary of the migration:\n\n## Migration Complete: Quarkus to Standalone Jakarta EE\n\n**Result: 67/67 smoke tests passing**\n\nThe RealWorld (Conduit) API has been successfully migrated from Quarkus to a standalone Jakarta EE stack:\n\n- **RESTEasy 6.2.12** for JAX-RS\n- **Weld SE 5.1.3** for CDI\n- **Hibernate ORM 6.6.4** for JPA\n- **Undertow 2.3.18** as the embedded HTTP server\n\n### Key challenges resolved during migration:\n\n1. **CDI injection** - Converted from Lombok constructor injection to CDI field injection for Weld proxy compatibility\n2. **Request scope** - Changed from `@RequestScoped` to `@Dependent` since Weld SE doesn't have servlet request context\n3. **EntityManager sharing** - Implemented `ThreadLocal<EntityManager>` pattern so all repositories within the same request share one EM instance\n4. **Transaction management** - Created `TransactionalInterceptor` with resource-local transactions, added `@Transactional` to all endpoints\n5. **Resource discovery** - Explicitly registered resources/providers via `setScannedResourceClasses`/`setScannedProviderClasses`\n6. **Jackson configuration** - Created `ObjectMapperContextResolver` for `WRAP_ROOT_VALUE`/`UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE`\n7. **Security** - Created `SecurityFilter` + `RolesAllowedFilter` for JWT auth and `@RolesAllowed` processing\n8. **Jandex conflict** - Excluded jandex 2.x from Weld, used smallrye jandex 3.2.0 for Hibernate 6.x compatibility","session_id":"4d21e41c-7b8c-412a-ac18-df8336bdf9ca","total_cost_usd":69.32200956000001,"usage":{"input_tokens":3968,"cache_creation_input_tokens":660458,"cache_read_input_tokens":25571473,"output_tokens":106677,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":660458}},"modelUsage"